<p>The 34-year-old New Zealand dancer seemed to stop for snacks before heading to rehearsal as she carried a bag from health food shop Kreation and a to-go cup. </p>

<p>Her husband, former Dancing With the Stars pro Maksim Chmerkovskiy stopped by the studio to visit his wife of three years. </p>

<p>The couple, who share a three-year-old son, shared a kiss in the parking lot. </p>

<p>Chmerkovskiy and Murgatroyd started a relationship in 2012 and announced their engagement in 2015 before welcoming a son and tying the knot in 2017. </p>

<p>Though Maksim will not be a pro on the upcoming season, Murgatroyd will be competing against her brother-in-law Val. </p>

